nnoremap k gk
nnoremap j gj

" Enter a blank line above and below the cursor.
" nnoremap [<space>  O<esc>j
" nnoremap ]<space>  o<esc>k
nnoremap <leader>k  O<esc>j
nnoremap <leader>j  o<esc>k

